    <title>第2章    信息的表示和处理</title>
    <link href="/2025/11/29/%E7%AC%AC2%E7%AB%A0%20%20%20%20%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/"/>
    <url>/2025/11/29/%E7%AC%AC2%E7%AB%A0%20%20%20%20%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="P31-图2-4"><a href="#P31-图2-4" class="headerlink" title="P31 图2-4"></a>P31 图2-4</h1><h6 id="c-语言代码示例"><a href="#c-语言代码示例" class="headerlink" title="c++语言代码示例"></a>c++语言代码示例</h6><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;cstddef&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iomanip&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> byte = <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">show_bytes</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">const</span> T&amp; x)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">const</span> byte* start = <span class="hljs-built_in">reinterpret_cast</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-type">const</span> byte*&gt;(&amp;x);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (std::<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="hljs-built_in">sizeof</span>(T); ++i) &#123;<br>        std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27; &#x27;</span><br>                  &lt;&lt; std::hex &lt;&lt; std::<span class="hljs-built_in">setw</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>) &lt;&lt; std::<span class="hljs-built_in">setfill</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>)<br>                  &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt;(start[i]);<br>    &#125;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; std::dec &lt;&lt; std::<span class="hljs-built_in">setfill</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27; &#x27;</span>) &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">test_show_bytes</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> val)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> ival = val;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">float</span> fval = <span class="hljs-built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-type">float</span>&gt;(val);<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> *pval = &amp;ival;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">show_bytes</span>(ival);   <br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">show_bytes</span>(fval);   <br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">show_bytes</span>(pval);   <br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val = <span class="hljs-number">12345</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">test_show_bytes</span>(val);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight tap"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs tap">输出结果：<br>39<span class="hljs-number"> 30 </span>00 00<br>00 e4<span class="hljs-number"> 40 </span>46<br>8c fe 5f<span class="hljs-number"> 00 </span>00<span class="hljs-number"> 00 </span>00 00<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看到原著中用3个show函数比较繁琐，故采用cpp中的模版简化代码。</p><h6 id="其中遇到了一些问题："><a href="#其中遇到了一些问题：" class="headerlink" title="其中遇到了一些问题："></a>其中遇到了一些问题：</h6><p>其一，是</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> byte = <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span>*;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在后面</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-type">const</span> byte start = <span class="hljs-built_in">reinterpret_cast</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-type">const</span> byte&gt;(&amp;x);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>报错</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql"><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;reinterpret_cast&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">type</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;const float*&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">to</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">type</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;byte&#x27;</span> &#123;aka <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;unsigned char*&#x27;</span>&#125; casts away qualifiers<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino">从<span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">float</span>*转成<span class="hljs-type">byte</span>，其类型发生改变。而<span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">byte</span>实际上是<span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span>* <span class="hljs-type">const</span>，意思是值可以改而指针不能改，上述操作把<span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">float</span>*改成了<span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *所以发生了casts away qualifiers。<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其二，是c++对字节的输出，这点确实没有c方便。<br>c++需要先把char转换成整数，然后用std::setw设置宽度为2，再用std::setfill填充0，还要用std::hex修改流状态为16进制，如此才能输出。<br>如果没有把char转换成int，会被operator &lt;&lt;按照字符处理，而不是整数，因为std::hex只影响整数格式化。</p><h1 id="练习题2-11"><a href="#练习题2-11" class="headerlink" title="练习题2.11"></a>练习题2.11</h1><h6 id="A"><a href="#A" class="headerlink" title="A"></a>A</h6><p>对于一个长度为奇数的数组，长度为 cnt &#x3D; 2k + 1，函数 reverse_array最后一次循环中，变量first和last的值是什么？<br>ans：值是k</p><h6 id="B"><a href="#B" class="headerlink" title="B"></a>B</h6><p>为什么这时（指<code>first == last</code>，即<code>&amp;a[first] == &amp;a[last]</code>）调用函数inplace_swap会将数组元素设置为0？<br>ans：因为此时first与last相同，导致传入inplace_swap的两个指针相同，在第一次异或运算后，该指针指向的值被置0，后面就是对0自身异或，结果仍是0</p><h6 id="C"><a href="#C" class="headerlink" title="C"></a>C</h6><p>对reverse_array的代码做哪些简单改动就能消除这个问题？<br>ans0：把&lt;&#x3D;中的&#x3D;去掉<br>ans1：上述方法治标不治本，我认为可以在inplace_swap函数中添加一行检测两指针是否相同且为空的代码，下面是我的改动</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">inplace_swap</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> *x,<span class="hljs-type">int</span> *y)</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(x == y || x == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span> || y == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>    *y = *x ^ *y;<br>    *x = *x ^ *y;<br>    *y = *x ^ *y;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">reverse_array</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a[],<span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt)</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> first,last;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(first = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>,last = cnt - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        first &lt; last;<br>        first++,last--)<br>    &#123;<br>        inplace_swap(&amp;a[first],&amp;a[last]);<br>        <br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// //Print debug information</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// printf(&quot;first = %d,last =%d, &quot;,first,last);</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// for(int i = 0; i &lt; cnt;++i)</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//     printf(&quot;%d &quot;,a[i]);</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// printf(&quot;\n&quot;);</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">test</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">array</span>[<span class="hljs-number">5</span>] = &#123;<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">5</span>&#125;;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> len = <span class="hljs-keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">array</span>)/<span class="hljs-keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>);<br>    reverse_array(<span class="hljs-built_in">array</span>,len);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;result = &quot;</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; len;++i)<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">array</span>[i]);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br>    test();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
